{"tid":1725523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無底線支持五四學生的北大校長蔡元培墓受損","createTime":"2019-11-15T18:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T19:19:17.000Z","uid":45975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"948860eb857cafae4c3713d1b08aeb3345ad4a7a","tid":1725523,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:38:42.000Z","msg":"RTHK<br />\n蔡元培在港墳墓遭破壞 有網民在微博承認事件<br />\n2019-11-16 HKT 02:19<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/3150/1*lfPkFeA6RwfPF6UlDlTIgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F3150%2F1%2AlfPkFeA6RwfPF6UlDlTIgg.png&h=e351b6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已故北京大學校長蔡元培位於香港的墳墓，懷疑遭人破壞。一名網民在內地微博發文，承認事件。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的微博帳號「哀極無淚」發文表示，他為「蔡元培的墓碑打磨了一下」，再在墓碑上，貼上兩名共產黨員汪壽華和趙世炎的遺像。<br />\n<br />\n該網民曾發文批評香港反修例示威，表示癱瘓港鐵的行動，內部是「有組織對抗中央」，​​​​又曾表示「段崇智也好，蔡元培也罷，大學校長們風度翩翩的外表下面，並不總代表社會的良知與正義」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社報道，蔡元培在任北大校長期間，催生「五四運動」，並與北洋軍閥周旋，以保護學生聞名，但因為涉及國民黨清黨的「412事件」，被部分左派分子視為殘殺共產黨員的幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sc.piee.pw/NP6NV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsc.piee.pw%2FNP6NV&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=e41aa1d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sc.piee.pw/NP6NV</a>"},{"pid":"b9912418ccb909f4fd440fe9449ea4ab8f1c414a","tid":1725523,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:39:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b4482237ccce8c02145a559088c46c0cd1412e6d","tid":1725523,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863c873be8924016432738bbd5c8abf51bf8e222","tid":1725523,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀&hellip;"},{"pid":"c451f1f244e91260d29b49e7f0317d00ddafa50b","tid":1725523,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:57:39.000Z","msg":"佢哋侮辱緊北大咋啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ddeb00d2fd48bac108b29936d9030c7bc1cbb0","tid":1725523,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T19:16:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1fa4dfbeb4d27d778a8c5031dcb97a3dd1c81b4e","tid":1725523,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T19:19:17.000Z","msg":"[事後檢討]請堅守原則，勿墮落為暴政魔警<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725525</a>"}]}